    "description": "《成为游戏》是一位年轻开发者和他的小团队独立开发的第一个项目。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390420/extras/5fa9c279688d29f9fcb6cc9bfeae4136.poster.avif?t=1704497277\" width=614 height=44 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390420/extras/5fa9c279688d29f9fcb6cc9bfeae4136.webm?t=1704497277\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390420/extras/5fa9c279688d29f9fcb6cc9bfeae4136.mp4?t=1704497277\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>你能拯救帝国吗？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390420/extras/8505ac944e90e45bf8ea8f5b066ec3c1.poster.avif?t=1704497277\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390420/extras/8505ac944e90e45bf8ea8f5b066ec3c1.webm?t=1704497277\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390420/extras/8505ac944e90e45bf8ea8f5b066ec3c1.mp4?t=1704497277\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><i>特点：</i></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390420/extras/ec6f77d9e292563d95e084a3cd757eb7.avif?t=1704497277\" width=620 height=80 /></span><br>探索一个广阔的开放世界，拥有多样化的景观和地区，享受独家沉浸式音乐和声音效果。发现独特的伙伴加入你的队伍并在战斗中帮助你。与动态经济互动，包括交易商品和管理你的商队。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390420/extras/72d4ea1d35541f5072a554850bca9e6f.avif?t=1704497277\" width=620 height=80 /></span><br>在战场上与数百名士兵进行实时战斗，指挥自己的军队，在史诗般的战斗中带领他们获胜。体验中世纪的武器、盔甲和建筑。在竞技场中为名誉和财富而战。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390420/extras/61dd1beccfc77101006623ed3c97e913.avif?t=1704497277\" width=620 height=80 /></span><br>用各种技能、装备和武器定制您的角色。完成各种派系和角色的任务，并建立自己的堡垒。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390420/extras/5e4fbded0b440e84a0acca34ba907f50.avif?t=1704497277\" width=620 height=80 /></span><br>您的英雄必须穿过人类和兽人的敌人大军，获得所需的力量和资源来击败终极敌人 - 皇帝本人。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390420/extras/8944195e477ee49beb86fe0197409365.poster.avif?t=1704497277\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390420/extras/8944195e477ee49beb86fe0197409365.webm?t=1704497277\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390420/extras/8944195e477ee49beb86fe0197409365.mp4?t=1704497277\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>一个混乱和冒险的世界等待着您，帝国的命运掌握在您手中。",
